snippet.title: New JD vs AH Transcripts or AH's Team: The Art of The Terrible Lie
snippet.description:
New transcripts are available in the Johnny Depp vs Amber Heard case in Fairfax and the amazing community has quickly spotted and called out AH's attorneys in many,  many lies and we talk about a few here.  

Link to Tiffany Daniels channel,  please go support 🙏 https://youtu.be/adm1IqFdkVA

You can help me with the expenses of running this channel and help with the expenses of attending the VA trial by donating to my PayPal at https://paypal.me/TammyTalksAbout?locale.x=en_US
